parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rupture of the airbag inflator can cause metal fragments to strike and potentially seriously injure the vehicle occupants.
symptoms: The airbag warning indicator illuminates and flashes
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the dashboard cracks or breaks
the airbag inflator housing ruptures.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A cracked or broken dashboard can cause the airbag to deploy improperly, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: The dashboard cracks or breaks
the airbag warning indicator illuminates and flashes
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of parts for the recall repair can leave the vehicle occupants at risk of serious injury or death due to airbag failure.
symptoms: The dealership is unable to obtain the necessary parts for the recall repair
the repair is delayed
the vehicle owner is unable to get the repair done.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can cause serious injury or death.

the vehicle occupants are injured or killed
the airbag warning indicator illuminates and flashes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the heater vents control flap can cause discomfort and distraction to the driver.

vehicle vibration
